{
  "id": "RAW_5ddd626a",
  "title": "不加算力，只改一个算法：Muon 在万亿 MoE 模型中最高 2 倍加速",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA3MzI4MjgzMw==&mid=2651024827&idx=2&sn=dc80269b563b462cf512c3754b935ba2",
  "date": "2026-03-31 05:36:00",
  "author": "机器之心",
  "siteName": "机器之心",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=7f01a959&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2F5L8bhP5dIqHZaicQWQGMM7O3hiatFTLb5MTPYxMCNhUI7RISdkmEBHfbSqU8CexBYnczUvKuwY1JM5vReTY0ricR5XYVXP7Qj1hKK3vhCHYyqI%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\" style=\"font-size: 1rem;\"></p>\n  <p>即插即用替换、几乎零成本</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\" nodeleaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.04259259259259259\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503523662\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=97ed75af&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2FKmXPKA19gW889cR13aBX42evqQIRibKlicoCrHPEpT0tQiceNphESCa2eJTqstP8G0yqMTkeMFrOGue6kOyCKdTkA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(153, 153, 153);\">机器之心编辑部</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在数值分析领域，Newton-Schulz 及其相关方法已被研究多年，但大多数工作关注的是高精度计算、CPU 优化或方阵输入。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">就在昨天，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">普林斯顿大学、纽约大学的四位研究者提出 Gram Newton-Schulz，通过重构 Newton-Schulz，使其更适配 GPU 和大模型训练场景，在万亿参数 MoE 模型中可将优化器时间降低 40–50%</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-aistatus=\"1\" data-imgfileid=\"503541146\" data-ratio=\"0.6296296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=58fa0bcc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHO3ToZ1p2eX4hqjg7ia4HokLAYELhkLibn5F1DBAH8coJiaOrl7HTqjhUYKeic7LdVU4FGNVxHnHXpxbibx6koeqVAWnj7AUTuVOmM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">我们用一句话来总结 Gram Newton-Schulz 的核心思想：</span></span></p>\n  <blockquote>\n   <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\">不再直接在矩阵 X∈R^n×m 上迭代，而是在更小的 Gram 矩阵 X X^⊤∈R^n×n 上迭代，从而降低计算量并利用对称矩阵计算优化。</span></p>\n  </blockquote>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">核心贡献包括如下：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">将标准 Newton-Schulz 重写为数学等价形式，主要作用在 n×n 空间；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">提出 Naive Gram Newton-Schulz（基础版本）；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">分析半精度下的不稳定性，并提出重启策略（Stabilized 版本）；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">实现对称矩阵乘法 GPU kernel；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">构建 GramMuon，在实际训练中实现 40–50% 加速且精度无损。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下图 1 为基于 NVIDIA B300 平台，AdamW 与 Muon 在 LLaMA 不同模型规模下的优化器步骤耗时（实际墙钟时间）对比。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6695747001090513\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"917\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541147\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=61ac2676&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGpbYb0pZfgBEialr4mQqiavaex84xj1LvyEtvMX5TyxN1MJyqjT8nKUBNjZN7mJp1h5HBuysAUGdgQLuX7g3ruD1RtQVL6WoIPk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">作者之一、普林斯顿大学本科生 Jack Zhang 表示，「我们让 Muon 在几乎不增加额外成本的情况下，运行速度最高提升 2 倍！Gram Newton-Schulz 可以作为 Muon 中 Newton-Schulz 的即插即用替代方案：我们观察到验证集困惑度几乎没有变化，误差在 0.01 以内。同时，我们也分享了在这一算法稳定化过程中的大量探索，确保在任何情况下都不牺牲训练质量。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.4089506172839505\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1296\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541149\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=187d8325&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEhRD6IhQ0sFqjuTnic4CJ5wOCBicKWBLuVzxuNmkBeq1jnC1khC7ibD078eCw5TjO67bfshC0kxaP4T3zlJsibfAgu46uic2QaRCyk%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">作者之一、普林斯顿大学助理教授、Together AI 联合创始人兼首席科学家 Tri Dao 表示，「这是我最喜欢的一类工作 —— 线性代数洞察 + 高性能算子。我们花了几个月时间，深入研究 Muon 中间过程里这些矩阵的特征值和特征向量，最终提出了一种简单而优雅的算法，让这一思路真正落地。」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.41388888888888886\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541150\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=77e257b3&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGqk7LXoafudetdxG4ltGKBw7Tdt34rp6NvgyrSbMA8nNx9RicARCtP4N1Nn3HRiaa6iboeph40HdkkFLHucN5mUbz8VS2Cs908ZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">接下来我们来看 Gram Newton-Schulz 相较于标准 Newton-Schulz 方法的优势。在此之前，有必要先回顾一下 Muon 优化器。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Muon 可以理解为在谱范数下的最速下降法：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2375249500998004\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1002\" style=\"width:329px;height:78px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541153\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c96e3e18&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEaxrZJzuatia7PI2iaCUuW3scgZgoLqqWlFPwMr1iaonfd81RXsFNwHV7fusVAQzqlXmGDQZoicUWNDKLtPr71MEuX8jL96FoiaTYc%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">其中：μ 表示动量系数，η 表示学习率，polar 表示极分解。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">极分解定义：若 X=UΣV^⊤，则：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.17445482866043613\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"642\" style=\"width:178px;height:31px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541154\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=095d2ef8&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHa79xibLeclBVSEmKDhxRhibBVoicFLZy8MtTkibI1xlJu0uGsFWaqYKWibO9uKEaCuPlQRsrGfTTtPyxKHce9Tiaw6IKic5bbYRyFW4%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">由于精确计算昂贵，Muon 使用 Newton-Schulz 进行近似。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">标准 Newton-Schulz 的迭代形式如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.13480885311871227\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"994\" style=\"width:282px;height:38px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541156\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=772694a0&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHSeGhJfXXJywNu8GLvwXznzz6XPzLsFTVUichKntiaSJa1F4sicWsRJibYHBBMnobwTvYoz121jfzkmxjILXhWDdc8DvyXnaQndss%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">本质上是对奇异值进行逐步归一化，使其趋向 1。不过，标准 Newton-Schulz 存在计算瓶颈。每轮迭代包含三次矩阵乘法：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">XX^⊤：2mn^2</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">A^2：2n^3</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">BX：2mn^2</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">总 FLOPs 如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.18584070796460178\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"904\" style=\"width:270px;height:50px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541157\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=8426bd6f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHWdQwjTxpcsxTglUDx9YbI64TibSZ42cqRw4kLapdEoAaFulHrebicQeibPLE4z8wkXicFfyS0WwxGW3ZiaicukYuLfepr9V6AuOAPA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这就导致了一些问题，包括大量矩形矩阵乘法（GPU 效率低） 、未利用对称性，并成为优化器瓶颈。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">因此，本文 Gram Newton-Schulz 核心思想是：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">将迭代从 X 转移到 Gram 矩阵</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.15326633165829145\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"796\" style=\"width:209px;height:32px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541158\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=311df971&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGn67Z0qpDHelmJQ1kW6XzCRbAQBR8yQ39xLCsP8SGmwHZ42NqBN9iaoXVrvQTJgiakiceHG9tJib0ZQNJmK4iaCMm1hJlrUY3F0Lo8%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">关键变换：任何奇数多项式</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.14541387024608501\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"894\" style=\"width:244px;height:35px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541159\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=ef575517&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGia9SqG6zSlQcpL0kr1aHfrQuXj4UxVZakuMczic10ChpCXQ8grM9Ps0iaODk5NedvhYnqSDYOLwdbspLibfkabib9ZqwKsVwbzUWQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">可写为</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.2041522491349481\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"578\" style=\"width:136px;height:28px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541160\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f12bd607&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqHOk1YfNDQSBVcNMZZDnKhznRaN58gIN7onPiawqBGBYQOdypUjqQGeich1t2CzKv6nFjWbWrewZCghV8U6ygTU7qWXPLia7yj5icA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这样一来，就将问题转为了 1）对 R 进行矩阵多项式迭代、 本质是近似 Y^-1/2。优势在于：维度从 n × m → n × n、可用对称矩阵乘法 kernel 以及 减少矩形 GEMM 次数。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">不过，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Naive Gram Newton-Schulz</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp;在 float16 下不稳定，Gram 矩阵可能产生负特征值，也会出现 loss spike 和 Inf。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.7138888888888889\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width:562px;height:401px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541161\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f0cc74ad&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGf6BZm77IxGNLdociaasyOpHJmuYy1s1v05yEW6ryoicP5iaA6scoZlAsm6BeJhzKjLib7ia7QC053as2LhlfzsoMjUu1RQ0ibNrDpM%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下图为 Llama-430M 上的 Naive Gram Newton-Schulz：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.6953703703703704\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541162\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f6bec5dc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFSwI4P8lP7MWibhiauRVbpxyfZRHY5iaOgCaeKvfODwkG7NR6W5pFXYTkvg5JK8Cut04Kicag21I2nJbqbvZ7ia4HMqrkWORlWcDls%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">因此有了</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">稳定版的 Stabilized Gram Newton-Schulz</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"1.1898148148148149\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541163\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=c4e9d444&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqFL0NiacWqcoCr5DLBoSXUjoLA3upvfAkYQ7TC62gjxlczU8zh1FgsZAjicv50MZgqYiapWQfgn95AOBaVeU9b7bo7X5bUBY0S4jA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">核心改进在于使用</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">&nbsp;float16 加速</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.3469387755102041\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"gif\" data-w=\"784\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541164\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5501d292&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2F5L8bhP5dIqHrczF22ux542r0e3fRZkNRyoqPZYGmWtiag8SWht5vrEZ6OmCP4ptWxWjpD8BSsRaqD4meS36n5EKHgtj6GavKH7K753J0ibx9s%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">并在第 2 步后重启：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.24521072796934865\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"522\" style=\"width:118px;height:29px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541165\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d03885cd&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqGI5YhJphXcAmSibI5m9QGVsicCPPqaxEz94lYx0zUbiczceM22HWpH20zAgSfb5jBx6ugHL0J3f97VhkIw4Z4NJjmYOTlvE7ibRxg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">以及重新初始化 Gram。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">结果显示，在保持稳定性的同时，仍然比原算法更快。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">标准 Newton-Schulz、Naive Gram 与 Stabilized Gram 的复杂度对比如下：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.8235294117647058\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"714\" style=\"width:217px;height:179px;\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541166\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=635973e6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqEXPu6m2x0qcHUj5V3sjJ9liabCfFfBsAD6a8wqX5kab2OF9ZdvyveITJ8EOVAe3015oENiahlY7qygxbWoSrOXcJ5v4XrYTNlNI%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">结果表明，当 α&gt;1（常见情况），Gram 方法明显更便宜，FLOPs 降低最高约 42%–58%。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">最后来看下 Gram Newton-Schulz 在 Kimi K2 中的耗时：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Kimi K2 是一个万亿参数级的稀疏、细粒度 MoE 模型，每一层包含 384 个专家，隐藏层维度为 7168，专家的中间层维度为 2048。由于模型正朝着更细粒度的 MoE 架构发展，且 Kimi K2 使用 Muon 进行训练，因此这是一个评测 Gram Newton-Schulz 的理想场景。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">团队将 Kimi K2 一次全局训练步骤中暴露出来的 Newton-Schulz 的墙钟时间，近似为以下部分的总和：</span></span></p>\n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">216 个专家的 up/gate/down 权重，形状为 2048 × 7168；</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">1 个 dense 的 up/gate/down 权重，形状为 7168 × 18432。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下图为 NVIDIA H100 Hopper 硬件上，在 Kimi K2 的流水线并行配置中，</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(61, 170, 214);font-weight: bold;\">Gram Newton-Schulz 的速度是标准 Newton-Schulz 的 2 倍</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.40185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541167\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=305603fe&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqG2wPiabaqjagKrVUE0qE3ppkhH2mMDkEbicTcFLxqq4wAkfuuSiaGYMLT4pibic91DTia4QJHWOQibM5H9icPUIONBqRD8bJ6SXWQia4Ag%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">下图为 NVIDIA B300 Blackwell 硬件上，在 Kimi K2 的流水线并行配置中，Gram Newton-Schulz 的速度同样是标准 Newton-Schulz 的 2 倍。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_insertlocalimg\" data-ratio=\"0.40185185185185185\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" type=\"block\" data-imgfileid=\"503541168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=1b0be82d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F5L8bhP5dIqG5e54xq0diaMc7nLjlyz5bEF1FYPBQr1p3Whrz99J4qGsqGbbj9kFBrv7nkumBQYuFkhgKXtxuu4VF4YaY0EELWEnR1Krb1jxA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">更多细节内容请参阅原博客。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.75em;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">博客地址：<a href=\"https://dao-lab.ai/blog/2026/gram-newton-schulz/\" target=\"_blank\">https://dao-lab.ai/blog/2026/gram-newton-schulz/</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文介绍了 Gram Newton-Schulz 算法，通过将 Muon 优化器的迭代过程转移到更小的 Gram 矩阵上，在万亿级 MoE 模型训练中实现了最高 2 倍的优化器加速。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文介绍了 Gram Newton-Schulz 算法，通过将 Muon 优化器的迭代过程转移到更小的 Gram 矩阵上，在万亿级 MoE 模型训练中实现了最高 2 倍的优化器加速。",
  "summary": "普林斯顿大学和纽约大学的研究者（包括 Tri Dao）提出了 Gram Newton-Schulz (GNS) 算法，旨在解决 Muon 优化器在 GPU 上进行极分解近似时的计算瓶颈。该方法的核心是将原本在权重矩阵上的迭代重构为在更小的 Gram 矩阵上进行，从而大幅减少 FLOPs 并能利用高效的对称矩阵乘法算子。针对 FP16 训练中的数值不稳定问题，研究团队提出了稳定版方案及重启策略。实验表明，在 Kimi K2 等万亿参数 MoE 模型中，该算法可将优化器耗时降低 40-50%，在 NVIDIA H100 和 B300 平台上实现显著的墙钟时间加速，且验证集精度无损。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "核心思想是将迭代从权重矩阵转移到 Gram 矩阵。",
      "explanation": "通过数学等价变换，将原本在 n×m 空间上的迭代转移到 n×n 空间，利用维度缩减显著降低计算量。"
    },
    {
      "point": "针对 GPU 硬件特性进行了深度优化。",
      "explanation": "将低效的矩形矩阵乘法（GEMM）替换为高效的对称矩阵乘法 kernel，充分释放 GPU 算力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "解决了半精度训练下的数值稳定性难题。",
      "explanation": "引入了稳定版算法及重启策略，有效处理了 FP16 格式下 Gram 矩阵可能出现的负特征值和溢出问题。"
    },
    {
      "point": "在万亿级 MoE 模型中实现了即插即用的无损加速。",
      "explanation": "在 Kimi K2 等真实大规模训练场景中，优化器耗时缩短一半，且验证集困惑度误差保持在 0.01 以内。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "不再直接在矩阵 X 上迭代，而是在更小的 Gram 矩阵 XXᵀ 上迭代，从而降低计算量并利用对称矩阵计算优化。",
    "Gram Newton-Schulz 可以作为 Muon 中 Newton-Schulz 的即插即用替代方案：我们观察到验证集困惑度几乎没有变化，误差在 0.01 以内。",
    "这是我最喜欢的一类工作 —— 线性代数洞察 + 高性能算子。"
  ],
